\begin_inset Formula $\covp{\varphi^{\prime}\bar{\varphi}^{\prime}}{1}\cdot\covp{\varphi^{\prime}\bar{\varphi}^{\prime}}{1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\covp{\varphi\bar{\varphi}}{1}\cdot\covp{\varphi^{\prime}\bar{\varphi}^{\prime}}{1}$
\end_inset

, and 
\begin_inset Formula $\covp{\varphi\varphi^{\prime}}{6}\cdot\covp{\bar{\varphi}\bar{\varphi}^{\prime}}{6}$
\end_inset

 as a complete set of independent quartic invariants.
 
